title: VeganEssentials.com
description: A large online vegan shop has its warehouse in Waukesha, where you can pick up any of the 2000+ all-vegan items found on the website. Save shipping costs by picking up your orders Mon-Fri 9am-5pm (by appointment only) or order online. Sells food, sweets, footwear, cosmetics, vitamins, body care, books, clothing and more.
